Dear <%= @invite.name %>,

We'd love to hear from you! We haven't received your RSVP yet for our wedding celebration in Provence.

You're invited to the following events:

<% @events.each do |event| %>
<%= event.name %>
<%= event.date&.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %><% if event.start_time %> at <%= event.start_time.strftime("%l:%M %p").strip %><% end %>
<% if event.location.present? %><%= event.location %><% end %>

<% end %>
Please take a moment to let us know if you can join us:
<%= @manage_url %>

<%= WEDDING[:couple_names] %>
example.wedding
